<h1>Welcome to Stickr!</h1>
<hr>
<p>Stickr is a website where you can create an account and upload pictures to the database for storage. To get started, simply click on "Sign up" to create a new account or "Sign in" to log in with an existing account. Once you are signed in, you can navigate to the Images tab on the navigation bar and add new images or view existing images. Currently, the application will only take image upload via web urls because it is being stored in the database as a text string.</p>
